Name: LANDING
checklistText:
1. Emer Drogue Fuse - ON
2. Check for Drogue Deploy
3. At appx. 20,000ft, Snorkel Ring - PULL
4. Emer O2 handle - EMER
5. Landing Bag switch - AUTO
6. Check main chute deploy
7. UHF/DF switch - R/T
8. Press Reg Handle - PULL
9. Check "Landing Bag" Telelight - GREEN
10. ASCS AC Bus switch - OFF
11. Photo Lights switch - OFF
